爱莎贝儿-148CM-L 粉肤 AHR029 伊月珊瑚Itsuki Sango-人间水蜜桃
她像一颗饱满多汁的水蜜桃，粉嫩诱人，指尖轻触时会微微颤动。
剥开她薄薄的外皮，内里甜腻的汁液会缓缓溢出，顺着曲线滑落，沾湿周遭的一切。
咬一口，汁水四溅，
甜中带涩，教人欲罢不能，
忍不住再深尝几分，直至那核儿被吮得光滑。

Elsa Babe-148CM-L Pink AHR029 Itsuki Sango-Human Peach
She's like a plump, juicy peach, pink and alluring, trembling slightly at the touch of your fingertips.
Peel back her thin skin, and the sweet, juicy inside slowly overflows, sliding down her curves and soaking everything around her.
Take a bite, and the juice bursts forth,
Sweet with a hint of astringency, irresistible,
You can't help but savor it a few more times, until the pit is sucked clean.
n: [Misc] Elsa Babe-148CM-L Pink AHR029 Itsuki Sango-Human Peach 爱莎贝儿-148CM-L 粉肤 AHR029 伊月珊瑚Itsuki Sango-人间水蜜桃
